HEADWORD: Circumpolar
<hw>Cir`cum*po"lar</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>circum-</ets> + <ets>polar</ets>.]</ety> <def>About the pole; --
applied to stars that revolve around the pole without setting; <as>as,
<ex>circumpolar</ex> stars</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

